.\" $FreeBSD$
Set to use
.Xr ccache 1
for the build.
No configuration is required except to install the
.Sy devel/ccache
package .
Using with
.Xr distcc 1
should set
.Sy CCACHE_PREFIX=distcc .
The default cache directory of ccache will be used, which can be overriden
with
.Sy CCACHE_DIR .
See
.Xr ccache 1
for more configuration options.
